, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995611668563, \"rank\": 4.3883328652967477e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inaugural Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"The proposal\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC Session\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the announcement, and the decision which will be taken by the IOC Session, work will begin on selecting a city and venue, the specific timing of the event, the titles to be included, the qualification process for the players and further details.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC Session\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"venue\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"the specific timing\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"the titles\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualification process\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"further details\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said that international federations already engaged in an e-version of their sport that is considered for inclusion in the Olympic Esports Games will be the IOC's first go-to partners.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3624217497529772e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3624217497529772e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"international federations\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"an e\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"version\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same will be true for National Olympic Committees that already include esports in their activities.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9973741408878458, \"rank\": 0.002632772401605109, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committees\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"esports\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"their activities\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, the IOC also announced plans to create a new dedicated structure within its organization, separate from the organizational and financial model for the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3624217497529772e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"a new dedicated structure\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"its organization\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizational and financial model\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to address the specific nature of the Olympic Esports Games, the IOC said it would take a different approach with regard to the financing and organization of these Games.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3624217497529772e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"the specific nature\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"a different approach\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"regard\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the financing\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"organization\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are very fortunate to be able to work with the Saudi NOC on the Olympic Esports Games, because it has great \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 if not unique \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 expertise in the field of esports with all its stakeholders.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.993706925872146, \"rank\": 0.006162654600704616, \"text\": \"Saudi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 expertise\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"esports\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"all its stakeholders\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Esports Games will greatly benefit from this experience,\\\" the IOC President Thomas Bach said.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.6434430287782554e-18, \"text\": \"Esports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\"}, {\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bac